oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Commencement invitation, 1915
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An invitation and envelope for the May/June 1915 commencement period; includes the class roll

The Senior Class of Middle Tennessee State Normal School invites you to be present at the fourth annual commencement Friday, May the twenty-eighth to Wednesday, June the second, nineteen hundred and fifteen. Murfreesboro, Tennessee.
